description: Retrieves information about all the applications that are associated with your Amazon Pinpoint account.

nested_items.name: ApplicationsResponse
nested_items.description: Provides information about all of your applications.

nested_items.name: Item
nested_items.description: An array of responses, one for each application that was returned.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the application.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the application. This identifier is displayed as the Project ID on the Amazon Pinpoint console.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The display name of the application. This name is displayed as the Project name on the Amazon Pinpoint console.

nested_items.name: CreationDate
nested_items.description: The date and time when the Application was created.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The string to use in a subsequent request to get the next page of results in a paginated response. This value is null if there are no additional pages.
